[% META
        title = "Node.js Implementation Summary"
   description = "Quick reference for Node.js v20 LTS integration in Comserv development, Docker, and CI/CD environments"
   roles = "developer,admin"
   TemplateType = "Documentation"
   category = "deployment"
   page_version = "1.0"
   last_updated = "Wed Oct 29 07:57:10 AM PDT 2025"
   site_specific = "false"
%]
[% PageVersion = 'Documentation/deployment/nodejs_implementation_summary.tt,v 1.0 07:57:10 2025/10/29 zencoder Exp - Node.js Implementation Summary' %]
[% IF c.session.debug_mode == 1 %]
    [% PageVersion %]
[% END %]

<div class="container">
    <h1 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">Node.js Implementation Summary</h1>
    
    <div class="last-updated" style="color: var(--text-muted-color); font-size: var(--font-size-small);">
        Last Updated: 2025-10-29 | 
        Version: 1.0 | 
        Author: Zencoder | 
        Status: Active
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-100">
            <h2 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">Quick Start (5 Minutes)</h2>
            <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">Get Node.js running immediately using the automated setup script:</p>
            
            <div style="background-color: var(--light-color); padding: var(--spacing-medium); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); margin: var(--spacing-small) 0;">
                <pre style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: monospace; margin: 0;"><code>
bash /home/shanta/PycharmProjects/comserv2/scripts/setup-nodejs.sh
                </code></pre>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-100">
            <h2 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">Architecture Overview</h2>
            <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">Node.js is integrated across three deployment tiers:</p>
            
            <div style="background-color: var(--light-color); padding: var(--spacing-medium); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); margin: var(--spacing-small) 0;">
                <pre style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: monospace; margin: 0;"><code>
PyCharm IDE (Local Development)
├─ Node.js 20 LTS Interpreter
├─ npm 10+
└─ Full IDE Integration
        ↓ (Shared Versions)
Docker Container (Consistency)
├─ Node.js 20 LTS
├─ npm 10+
└─ Agent Runtime Environment
        ↓ (CI/CD Pipeline)
Production Deployment
├─ Consistent Node.js v20
├─ All Teams Same Versions
└─ package-lock.json Locked
                </code></pre>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-50">
            <h2 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">Local Setup Steps</h2>
            <ol style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                <li>Install Node.js v20 LTS via NodeSource</li>
                <li>Install project dependencies with npm</li>
                <li>Configure PyCharm Node interpreter</li>
                <li>Restart PyCharm and verify</li>
                <li>Test with <code>node --version</code></li>
            </ol>
        </div>
        <div class="col-50">
            <h2 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">Docker Setup Steps</h2>
            <ol style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                <li>Update Comserv/Dockerfile (add Node.js installation)</li>
                <li>Rebuild Docker images with <code>docker-compose build --no-cache</code></li>
                <li>Verify with <code>docker-compose exec web-dev node --version</code></li>
                <li>Test agent environment</li>
                <li>Commit changes to git</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-100">
            <h2 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">Implementation Commands</h2>
            
            <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); font-size: var(--font-size-large);">Local Installation</h3>
            <div style="background-color: var(--light-color); padding: var(--spacing-medium); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); margin: var(--spacing-small) 0;">
                <pre style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: monospace; margin: 0;"><code>
# Step 1: Install Node.js
curl -fsSL https://deb.nodesource.com/setup_20.x | sudo -E bash -
sudo apt-get install -y nodejs

# Step 2: Install project dependencies
cd /home/shanta/PycharmProjects/comserv2
npm install

# Step 3: Verify
node --version  # v20.x.x
npm --version   # 10.x.x
                </code></pre>
            </div>

            <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); font-size: var(--font-size-large);">Docker Integration</h3>
            <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">Update Comserv/Dockerfile at both line 22 (builder) and line 49 (runtime):</p>
            <div style="background-color: var(--light-color); padding: var(--spacing-medium); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); margin: var(--spacing-small) 0;">
                <pre style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: monospace; margin: 0;"><code>
# Install Node.js LTS
RUN curl -fsSL https://deb.nodesource.com/setup_20.x | bash - && \
    apt-get install -y nodejs && \
    npm install -g npm@latest && \
    rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
                </code></pre>
            </div>

            <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">Then rebuild:</p>
            <div style="background-color: var(--light-color); padding: var(--spacing-medium); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); margin: var(--spacing-small) 0;">
                <pre style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: monospace; margin: 0;"><code>
docker-compose build --no-cache
docker-compose exec web-dev node --version
                </code></pre>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-100">
            <h2 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">PyCharm Configuration</h2>
            <ol style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                <li>Open <strong>File > Settings > Languages &amp; Frameworks > Node.js and NPM</strong></li>
                <li>Click folder icon next to "Node interpreter:"</li>
                <li>Select "Add" → "Add Local"</li>
                <li>Set path to <strong>/usr/bin/node</strong></li>
                <li>Set npm to <strong>/usr/bin/npm</strong></li>
                <li>Click OK and restart PyCharm</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-100">
            <h2 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">Verification Checklist</h2>
            <ul style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                <li>☐ Node.js v20 LTS installed (<code>node --version</code>)</li>
                <li>☐ npm v10+ installed (<code>npm --version</code>)</li>
                <li>☐ PyCharm Node interpreter configured</li>
                <li>☐ <code>package.json</code> created and dependencies installed</li>
                <li>☐ <code>.env.agents</code> file created</li>
                <li>☐ Dockerfile updated with Node.js installation</li>
                <li>☐ Docker images rebuilt successfully</li>
                <li>☐ Node.js available in Docker container</li>
                <li>☐ Can run: <code>npm start</code> in project directory</li>
                <li>☐ All team members verified their local setup</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-100">
            <h2 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">Testing Node.js Setup</h2>
            
            <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); font-size: var(--font-size-large);">Local Testing</h3>
            <div style="background-color: var(--light-color); padding: var(--spacing-medium); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); margin: var(--spacing-small) 0;">
                <pre style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: monospace; margin: 0;"><code>
# Test Node.js availability
node --version
npm --version

# Test agent environment
npm run dev

# List installed agents
npm run list-agents
                </code></pre>
            </div>

            <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); font-size: var(--font-size-large);">Docker Testing</h3>
            <div style="background-color: var(--light-color); padding: var(--spacing-medium); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); margin: var(--spacing-small) 0;">
                <pre style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: monospace; margin: 0;"><code>
# Test in container
docker-compose exec web-dev node --version
docker-compose exec web-dev npm --version

# Test agent runtime
docker-compose up web-dev
                </code></pre>
            </div>

            <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); font-size: var(--font-size-large);">PyCharm Testing</h3>
            <ol style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                <li>Open PyCharm Terminal</li>
                <li>Run: <code>node --version</code></li>
                <li>Should see: <code>v20.x.x</code></li>
                <li>Create a .js file and check for language support</li>
                <li>JavaScript syntax highlighting should work</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-100">
            <h2 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">Environment Consistency</h2>
            <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">All developers and deployment environments use:</p>
            <ul style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                <li><strong>Node.js</strong>: v20 LTS (Long Term Support)</li>
                <li><strong>npm</strong>: v10+</li>
                <li><strong>Package Lock</strong>: package-lock.json committed to git</li>
                <li><strong>CI/CD</strong>: npm ci for reproducible installations</li>
                <li><strong>Development</strong>: npm install for flexibility</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-100">
            <h2 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">Files Created/Modified</h2>
            
            <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); font-size: var(--font-size-large);">New Files</h3>
            <ul style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                <li><strong>scripts/setup-nodejs.sh</strong> - Automated setup script</li>
                <li><strong>package.json</strong> - Project dependencies (to be created)</li>
                <li><strong>.env.agents</strong> - Agent environment configuration</li>
                <li><strong>agents/index.js</strong> - Agent loader entry point (to be created)</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); font-size: var(--font-size-large);">Modified Files</h3>
            <ul style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                <li><strong>Comserv/Dockerfile</strong> - Add Node.js installation to builder and runtime stages</li>
                <li><strong>docker-compose.yml</strong> - (No changes needed, just rebuild images)</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-100">
            <h2 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">Next Steps</h2>
            <ol style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                <li>Run automated setup script or follow manual steps</li>
                <li>Configure PyCharm Node interpreter</li>
                <li>Update Dockerfile with Node.js installation</li>
                <li>Create package.json with agent dependencies</li>
                <li>Rebuild Docker images</li>
                <li>Verify setup with provided checklist</li>
                <li>Commit all changes to git</li>
                <li>Share setup steps with team members</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-100">
            <h2 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">Resources</h2>
            <ul style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                <li><strong>Detailed Setup Guide</strong>: See <code>nodejs_setup_guide.tt</code></li>
                <li><strong>Node.js Official Docs</strong>: https://nodejs.org/docs/</li>
                <li><strong>npm Documentation</strong>: https://docs.npmjs.com/</li>
                <li><strong>Zencoder Integration</strong>: Update .qodo agent definitions after setup</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

</div>